return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2017-10-31 23:08:01+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=2; plural=n != 1;','project-id-version'=>'WordPress - 4.9.x - Administration - Network Admin','language'=>'jv_ID','messages'=>['Network'=>'Jaringan','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Tools_Network_Screen">Documentation on the Network Screen</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Tools_Network_Screen">Dokumentasi kanggo Layar Jaringan</a>','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Create_A_Network">Documentation on Creating a Network</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Create_A_Network">Dokumentasi kanggo Cara nggawé Jaringan</a>','The choice of subdirectory sites is disabled if this setup is more than a month old because of permalink problems with &#8220;/blog/&#8221; from the main site. This disabling will be addressed in a future version.'=>'Pilihan subdirektori situs uwis dipaténi yén setélan iki luwih sākā sewulan suwéné jalaran masalah permalink karo  &#8220;/blog/&#8221; sākā situs utāmā. Matiné iki bakal dialamataké nang versi sklanjuté.','Once you add this code and refresh your browser, multisite should be enabled. This screen, now in the Network Admin navigation menu, will keep an archive of the added code. You can toggle between Network Admin and Site Admin by clicking on the Network Admin or an individual site name under the My Sites dropdown in the Toolbar.'=>'Sepisanan Sampéyan nambah kode iki lan nganyari peramban Sampéyan, multi situs kuduné langsung urip. Layar iki, saiki menu navigasi Admin Jaringan, bakalan njagani arsip sākā kode sing ditambahaké. Sampéyan bisā wolak-walik sākā Admin Jaringan lan Admin Situs karo ngeklik nang Admin Jaringan utāwā nang jeneng situsé nganggo menu keréh SitusKu.','Add the designated lines of code to wp-config.php (just before <code>/*...stop editing...*/</code>) and <code>.htaccess</code> (replacing the existing WordPress rules).'=>'Tambahaké rancangan baris kode marang wp-config.php (sakdurungé <code>/*...stop nyunting...*/</code>) lan <code>.htaccess</code> (Ngganti parāgā WordPress sing cumawis).','The next screen for Network Setup will give you individually-generated lines of code to add to your wp-config.php and .htaccess files. Make sure the settings of your FTP client make files starting with a dot visible, so that you can find .htaccess; you may have to create this file if it really is not there. Make backup copies of those two files.'=>'Layar saklanjuté kanggo Setup Jaringan bakal ménéhi Sampéyan baris kode dhéwé-dhéwé kanggo nambahi wp-config.php Sampéyan lan berkas .htaccess. Pestèkaké setélan klien FTP Sampéyan gawé berkas dimulai nganggo titik sing katon, mengkoné Sampéyan bisā nemokaké .htaccess; Sampéyan bisā gawé berkas iki yén pancén berkasé ora ānā nang kānā. Gawénānā salinan backup sākā rong berkas iku.','Choose subdomains or subdirectories; this can only be switched afterwards by reconfiguring your installation. Fill out the network details, and click Install. If this does not work, you may have to add a wildcard DNS record (for subdomains) or change to another setting in Permalinks (for subdirectories).'=>'Pilih subdomain utāwā subdirektori; iki namung bisa dituker sakwisé ngonfigurasi ulang instalasi. Isenānā detil jaringan, lan klik install. Yén iki ora mlaku, Sampéyan kudu nambahi rekod DNS wildcard (kanggo subdomain) utāwā ganti nganggo setélan liyane nang Permalink (kanggo subdirektori).','This screen allows you to configure a network as having subdomains (<code>site1.example.com</code>) or subdirectories (<code>example.com/site1</code>). Subdomains require wildcard subdomains to be enabled in Apache and DNS records, if your host allows it.'=>'Laman iki Ngidinaké Sampéyan kanggo ngatur jaringan sing nduwéni subdomain (<code>site1.example.com</code>) utāwā subdirektori (<code>example.com/site1</code>). Subdomain mbutuhaké tandha wildcard subdomain kanggo nguripaké nang Apache lan rekod DNS, yèn host Sampéyan ngidinaké.','Create a Network of WordPress Sites'=>'Gawe Jaringan sākā Situs Wordpress','You must define the %1$s constant as true in your %2$s file to allow creation of a Network.'=>'Sampéyan kudu netepi konstanta %1$s dadi true nang berkas %2$s sampéyan kanggo ngidinaké gawé Jaringan.','The Network creation panel is not for WordPress MU networks.'=>'Panel kreasi Jaringan iki dudu kanggo jaringan Wordpress MU.','Users deleted.'=>'Panganggo dibusak.','Users removed from spam.'=>'Panganggo dipindah sākā spam.','Users marked as spam.'=>'Panganggo di paringi tondo spam.','You can make an existing user an additional super admin by going to the Edit User profile page and checking the box to grant that privilege.'=>'Sampéyan bisa ndadékaké panganggo sing wis cumawis dadi super admin karo nyunting nang kācā profil Panganggo lan nyènthang kothak pilih kanggo ngakui kawenangané.','The bulk action will permanently delete selected users, or mark/unmark those selected as spam. Spam users will have posts removed and will be unable to sign up again with the same email addresses.'=>'Aksi borongan bakal mbusak selawasé panganggo sing dipilih, utāwā nandhani/ora nandhani sing kepilih dadi spam. Panganggo spam nduwéni pos sing bakal dibusak lan ora bakal bisā ndaftar manéh nganggo alamat emil sing pādhā.','You can sort the table by clicking on any of the table headings and switch between list and excerpt views by using the icons above the users list.'=>'Sampéyan bisā ngurutaké tabel karo ngeklik nang sembarang sesirahan tabel lan dituker antarané daftar lan tampilan kutipan nganggo ikon sing nang ndhuwuré daftar panganggo.','You can also go to the user&#8217;s profile page by clicking on the individual username.'=>'Sampéyan ugā bisā nuju marang kācā profil panganggo karo ngeklik nang jeneng panganggoné.','Hover over any user on the list to make the edit links appear. The Edit link on the left will take you to their Edit User profile page; the Edit link on the right by any site name goes to an Edit Site screen for that site.'=>'Obahaké mouse nang ndhuwuré daftar panganggo kanggo nontonaké pranālā sunting. Pranālā sunting nang sebelah kiwā bisā kanggo nyunting kācā profil Panganggo; Pranāla sunting nang sebelah tengen kanggo Nyunting Situs laman situsé.','This table shows all users across the network and the sites to which they are assigned.'=>'Tabel iki nontanaké kabeh panganggo nang sumebaring jaringan lan situs endi sing ndaftari.','Warning! User cannot be modified. The user %s is a network administrator.'=>'Pengetan! Panganggo iki ora bisā diowahi. Panganggo %s iki administrator jaringan.','User added. <a href="%s">Edit user</a>'=>'Panganggo wis ditambahaké. <a href="%s">Sunting panganggo</a>','Cannot add user.'=>'Ora bisā nambah panganggo.','Cannot create an empty user.'=>'Ora bisā nggawé panganggo kothong.','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Users_Screen">Documentation on Network Users</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Users_Screen">Dokumentasi kanggo Panganggo Jaringan</a>','Users who are signed up to the network without a site are added as subscribers to the main or primary dashboard site, giving them profile pages to manage their accounts. These users will only see Dashboard and My Sites in the main navigation until a site is created for them.'=>'Panganggo sing ndaftar jaringan tanpā liwat situs ditambahaké dadi subscriber marang dasbor situs utama utāwā primer, diwénéhi kācā profil kanggo ngatur akuné. Panganggo-panganggo iki namung bisa nonton Dasbor lan Situsku nang navigasi utama nganti ānā situs sing digawé.','Add User will set up a new user account on the network and send that person an email with username and password.'=>'Nambah panganggo bakal nyetèl akun panganggo anyar nang jaringan lan ngirim wong kuwi email sing isiné jeneng panganggo lan sandhi.','WordPress has been updated! Before we send you on your way, we need to individually upgrade the sites in your network.'=>'WordPress uwis dianyari! Sakdurungé kula ngirim sampeyan nang jaluré, kula mbutuhaké upgrade kepisah nang jaringan sampeyan.','Next Sites'=>'Situs Saklanjuté','If your browser doesn&#8217;t start loading the next page automatically, click this link:'=>'Yèn peramban Sampéyan ora mulai ngemot otomatis kācā saklanjuté, klik pranālā iki:','Warning! Problem updating %1$s. Your server may not be able to connect to sites running on it. Error message: %2$s'=>'Weling! Ana masalah nalika nganyari %1$s. Server sampéyan mungkin ora bisā nyambung karo situs sing mlaku. Pesen kaluputan: %2$s','All done!'=>'Kabeh Rampung!','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Updates_Screen">Documentation on Upgrade Network</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Updates_Screen">Dokumentsi kanggo nganyari Jaringan</a>','If this process fails for any reason, users logging in to their sites will force the same update.'=>'Yèn proses iki gagal amargā ānā sebab tinentu, panganggo sing mlebu log nang situsé bakal dipeksa nganggo update sing padha.','If a version update to core has not happened, clicking this button won&#8217;t affect anything.'=>'Yèn versi update inti ora dadi, ngeklik tombol iki ora bakal pengaruh āpā-āpā.','Only use this screen once you have updated to a new version of WordPress through Updates/Available Updates (via the Network Administration navigation menu or the Toolbar). Clicking the Upgrade Network button will step through each site in the network, five at a time, and make sure any database updates are applied.'=>'Namung ping pisan nganggo layar iki Sampéyan kudu ngupdate versi anyar WordPress liwat Update/Update sing cumawis(liwat nmenu navigasi Administrasi Jaringan utāwā bilah piranti). Ngeklik tombol Upgrade Jaringan bakal nglangkahi saben situs nang jaringan iki, ping limā sekaligus, lan pestékaké saben update database bakal ditrapaké.','You cannot delete a theme while it is active on the main site.'=>'Sampéyan ora bisā mbusak tema nalika temane aktif dadi tema situs.','%s theme deleted.'=>'tema %s dibusak.' . "\0" . 'tema-tema %s dibusak.','Themes list navigation'=>'Navigasi Daftar tulisan','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Themes_Screen">Documentation on Network Themes</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Themes_Screen">Dokumentas kanggo Tema Jaringan</a>','Themes can be enabled on a site by site basis by the network admin on the Edit Site screen (which has a Themes tab); get there via the Edit action link on the All Sites screen. Only network admins are able to install or edit themes.'=>'Tema bisa diuripaké nang situs dening admin jaringan nang layar Sunting Situs (sing nduwéni tab Tema); Tiliki mrānā liwat pranālā Sunting nang sakabèhing layar Situs. Kudu admin jaringan sing bisā masang utāwā nyunting tema-tema.','If the network admin disables a theme that is in use, it can still remain selected on that site. If another theme is chosen, the disabled theme will not appear in the site&#8217;s Appearance > Themes screen.'=>'Yèn admin jaringan maténi tema sing lagi dienggo, kuwi tetep bisa dipilih nang situs iku. Yèn tema liyané sing dipilih, tema sing dipaténi ora bakal ditampilaké nang Pakeliran situs > Laman Tema.','This screen enables and disables the inclusion of themes available to choose in the Appearance menu for each site. It does not activate or deactivate which theme a site is currently using.'=>'Layar iki nguripaké lan maténi kalebu tema-tema sing cumawis kanggo dipilih nang menu Pakeliran nang saben situs. Iki ora aktif utāwā non aktif nang tema sing saiki dienggo.','No, return me to the theme list'=>'Ora, balekaké aku nang daftar tema','Yes, delete these themes'=>'Iyā, busaki tema-tema iki','Yes, delete this theme'=>'Ya, busak tema iki','Are you sure you wish to delete these themes?'=>'Sampéyan yakin arep mbusak tema iki?','Are you sure you wish to delete this theme?'=>'Sampéyan yakin arep mbusak tema iki?','theme%1$s by %2$s'=>'%1$s by %2$s','You are about to remove the following themes:'=>'Sampéyan nembé waé mbuwang tema-tema iki:','These themes may be active on other sites in the network.'=>'Tema iki mungkin aktif nang situs liya nang jarungan iki.','Delete Themes'=>'Mbusak Tema','You are about to remove the following theme:'=>'Sampéyan nembé waé mbuwang tema-tema iki:','This theme may be active on other sites in the network.'=>'Tema iki mungkin aktif neng situs liya nang jaringan iki.','Delete Theme'=>'Mbusak Tema','Sorry, you are not allowed to delete themes for this site.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké mbusak tema situs iki.','Sorry, you are not allowed to manage network themes.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké natani tema jaringan.','Site marked as spam.'=>'Situs ditandhani spam.','Site removed from spam.'=>'Situs dipindah sākā spam.','Site deactivated.'=>'Situs ora diaktifaké.','Site activated.'=>'Situs diaktifaké.','Site unarchived.'=>'Situs ora diarsip.','Site archived.'=>'Situs diarsip.','Sorry, you are not allowed to delete that site.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké mbusak situs iki.','Site deleted.'=>'Situs dibusak.','Sites deleted.'=>'Situs-situs dibusak.','Sites marked as spam.'=>'Situs ditandhani dadi spam.','Sites removed from spam.'=>'Situs dipindah sākā spam.','You are about to delete the following sites:'=>'Sampéyan arep mbusaki situs-situs iki:','Sorry, you are not allowed to delete the site %s.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké mbusak situs %s.','Confirm'=>'Konfirmasi','Confirm your action'=>'Ngonfirmasi tindakan sampéyan','Sorry, you are not allowed to change the current site.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké ngowahi situs iki.','The requested action is not valid.'=>'Aksi sing dijaluk ora cocog.','You are about to mark the site %s as not mature.'=>'Sampéyan nembé waé nandhani situs %s dudu situs dewasa.','You are about to mark the site %s as mature.'=>'Sampéyan nembé waé nandhani situs %s kalebu situs dewasa.','You are about to delete the site %s.'=>'Sampéyan bisā mbusak situs %s.','You are about to mark the site %s as spam.'=>'Sampéyan bisā nandhani spam marang situs %s iki .','You are about to unspam the site %s.'=>'Sampéyan bisā ngilangi tandha spam marang situs %s iki.','You are about to archive the site %s.'=>'Sampéyan bisā ngarsipaké situs %s iki.','You are about to unarchive the site %s.'=>'Sampéyan bisā mbuwang arsip marang situs %s iki.','You are about to deactivate the site %s.'=>'Sampéyan nembé waé maténi situs %s.','You are about to activate the site %s.'=>'Sampéyan nembé waé nguripaké situs %s.','Sites list'=>'Daftar situs','Sites list navigation'=>'Navigasi Daftar situs','Clicking on bold headings can re-sort this table.'=>'Ngeklik nang Irah-irahan kandel bisā ngurutaké tabel iki.','The site ID is used internally, and is not shown on the front end of the site or to users/viewers.'=>'ID situs iki dienggo internal, lan ora ditontonaké nang kācā ngarep situs utāwā panganggo/tamu.','Visit to go to the front-end site live.'=>'Niliki marang kācā ngarep situs sing mlaku.','Delete which is a permanent action after the confirmation screens.'=>'Mbusaki iki aksi permanen sing dilakokaké sakwisé layar konfirmasi.','Deactivate, Archive, and Spam which lead to confirmation screens. These actions can be reversed later.'=>'Non aktifaké, ngarsip, lan Spam bakal dituntun nganggo layar konfirmasi. Aksi-aksi iki ora bisā dibalekaké.','Dashboard leads to the Dashboard for that site.'=>'Dasbor bakal nuntun mlebu nang Dasbor situs iki.','An Edit link to a separate Edit Site screen.'=>'Pranālā Nyunting kanggo layar Sunting Situs sing dipisah.','Hovering over each site reveals seven options (three for the primary site):'=>'Ngobahke mouse neng nduwure saben jeneng situs bakal ngatonke 7 pilihan (3 kanggo situs utāmā)','This is the main table of all sites on this network. Switch between list and excerpt views by using the icons above the right side of the table.'=>'Iki tabel utāmā sākā kabeh situs neng jaringan iki. Ngganti sākā sing katon namung daftar utāwā ugā katon petikane nganggo simbol neng nduwure tabel sisih tengen.','Add New takes you to the Add New Site screen. You can search for a site by Name, ID number, or IP address. Screen Options allows you to choose how many sites to display on one page.'=>'Tambah Anyar nggāwā Sampéyan nuju layar Tambah Situs Anyar. Sampéyan bisā nggolèki jeneng Situs, nomer ID, utāwā alamat IP. Opsi Layar ngidinaké Sampéyan kanggo milih jumlah situs sing arep ditampilaké nang kācā.','A password reset link will be sent to the user via email.'=>'Pranālā nyetél ulang tembung sandhi dikirimmarang panganggo liwat email.','Add User'=>'Tambah panganggo','Duplicated username or email address.'=>'Jeneng panganggo utāwā alamat email ānā sing ngembari.','Enter the username and email.'=>'Lebokaké jeneng panganggo utāwā alamat email.','User created.'=>'Pangangggo wis digawé.','Select a user to remove.'=>'Pilih panganggo kanggo dibusak.','Select a user to change role.'=>'Pilih panganggo kanggo diganti parāgāné.','Enter the username of an existing user.'=>'Leboknā jeneng panganggo sākā panganggo sing wis ānā.','User could not be added to this site.'=>'Panganggo ora bisā ditambahaké marang situs iki.','User is already a member of this site.'=>'Panganggo uwis dadi anggota nang situs iki.','Site users list'=>'Daftar situs panganggo','Site users list navigation'=>'Navigasi daftar situs pengguna','Filter site users list'=>'Daftar filter situs panganggo','Network enabled themes are not shown on this screen.'=>'Tema jaringan sing diuripaké ora ditontonaké nang layar iki.','No theme selected.'=>'Ora ānā tema sing dipilih.','%s theme disabled.'=>'tema %s dipaténi.' . "\0" . 'tema-tema %s dipaténi.','Theme disabled.'=>'Tema dipateni.','%s theme enabled.'=>'tema %s diuripaké.' . "\0" . 'tema-tema %s diuripaké.','Theme enabled.'=>'Tema diuripaké.','Site themes list'=>'Daftar tema situs','Site themes list navigation'=>'Navigasi daftar tema situs','Filter site themes list'=>'Daftar filter tema situs','Sorry, you are not allowed to manage themes for this site.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké natani tema kanggo situs iki.','Site options updated.'=>'Opsi situs wis dianyari.','Add Site'=>'Nambah Situs','The username and a link to set the password will be mailed to this email address.'=>'Jeneng panganggo lan pranālā setèlan tembung sandhi bakal dikirim neng alamat email iki.','A new user will be created if the above email address is not in the database.'=>'Salah siji ning panganggo anyar bakal digawé menāwā alamat email neng nduwur durung ānā neng database.','Admin Email'=>'Email Admin','Only lowercase letters (a-z), numbers, and hyphens are allowed.'=>'Namung huruf cilik (a-z), angka, lan tandha hubung sing diidinaké.','Add New Site'=>'Tambah Situs Anyar','Site added. <a href="%1$s">Visit Dashboard</a> or <a href="%2$s">Edit Site</a>'=>'Situs wis ditambahaké. <a href="%1$s">Tiliki Dasbor</a> utāwā <a href="%2$s">Nyunting Situs</a>','email "From" fieldSite Admin'=>'Admin Situs','New site created by %1$s

