Jeneng: %3$s','[%s] New Site Created'=>'[%s] Situs Anyar Wis Digawé','There was an error creating the user.'=>'Ānā kaluputan wayah nggawé panganggo.','The domain or path entered conflicts with an existing username.'=>'Domain utāwā pang sing dilebokaké satru karo jeneng panganggo sing wis cumawis.','Missing email address.'=>'Alamat email ilang.','Missing or invalid site address.'=>'Alamat situs ora valid utāwā ilang.','The following words are reserved for use by WordPress functions and cannot be used as blog names: %s'=>'Tembung-tembung iki dicadangaké kanggo jeneng fungsi-fungsi WordPress lan ora bisā digunakaké dadi jeneng blog: %s','Can&#8217;t create an empty site.'=>'Ora bisā nggawé situs kothongan.','If the admin email for the new site does not exist in the database, a new user will also be created.'=>'Yèn email admin kanggo situs anyar ora ānā nang database, panganggo anyar uga bakal tetep digawé.','This screen is for Super Admins to add new sites to the network. This is not affected by the registration settings.'=>'Laman iki kanggo Super Admin kanggo nambah situs anyar nang jaringan. Iki ora ngaruhi marang setélan pendaftaran.','Sorry, you are not allowed to add sites to this network.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké nambahi situs marang jaringan iki.','Set site attributes'=>'Nyetèl atribut situs','Attributes'=>'Atribut','Edit Site: %s'=>'Sunting Situs: %s','Site info updated.'=>'Indo situs uwis dianyari.','The requested site does not exist.'=>'Situs sing dijaluk ora cumawis.','Invalid site ID.'=>'ID situs ora cocog.','Sorry, you are not allowed to edit this site.'=>'Pangapurané, Sampéyan ora diidinaké nyunting situs iki.','Enable menus'=>'Nguripaké menu','Enable administration menus'=>'Nguripaké menu administrasi','Default Language'=>'Bāsā Standar','Language Settings'=>'Setèlan Bāsā','Size in kilobytes'=>'Ukuran nang kilobytes','%s KB'=>'%s KB','Max upload file size'=>'Ukuran maksimal berkas unggahan','Allowed file types. Separate types by spaces.'=>'Jenis berkas sing diidinaké. Pisahaké tipe nganggo spasi.','Upload file types'=>'Tipe unggahan berkas','Limit total size of files uploaded to %s MB'=>'Batesan ukuran berkas sing bisā diunggahne %s MB','Site upload space'=>'Kapasitas unggahan situs','Upload Settings'=>'Pangaturan Unggahan','The URL for the first comment on a new site.'=>'URL kanggo pangalembānā kapisan neng situs anyar.','First Comment URL'=>'URL Pangalembānā Kapisan','The email address of the first comment author on a new site.'=>'Alamat email pangarang komentar pisanan ing situs anyar.','First Comment Email'=>'Email Komentar Pertama','The author of the first comment on a new site.'=>'Panulis sākā pangalembānā kapisan neng situs anyar.','First Comment Author'=>'Panulis Pangalembānā Kapisan','The first comment on a new site.'=>'Pangalembānā Kapisan neng situs anyar.','First Comment'=>'Pangalembānā Kapisan','The first page on a new site.'=>'Kācā kapisan neng situs anyar.','First Page'=>'Kācā Kapisan','The first post on a new site.'=>'Tulisan kapisan neng situs anyar.','The welcome email sent to new users.'=>'Email sugeng rawuh dikirim neng panganggo anyar.','Welcome User Email'=>'Email Sugeng Rawuh Panganggo','The welcome email sent to new site owners.'=>'Email sugeng rawuh dikirim neng sing duwe situs.','Welcome Email'=>'Email Sugeng Rawuh','New Site Settings'=>'Setélan Situs Anyar','If you want to ban domains from site registrations. One domain per line.'=>'Yèn sampèyan péngin mblokir domain sākā pendaftaran situs. Siji domain per baris.','Banned Email Domains'=>'Domain Email sing Diblokir','If you want to limit site registrations to certain domains. One domain per line.'=>'Yèn sampèyan péngin mbatesi pendaftaran situs marang domain tinentu. Siji domain per baris.','Limited Email Registrations'=>'Pendaftaran Email mung-mungan','Users are not allowed to register these sites. Separate names by spaces.'=>'Panganggo ora diidinaké ndaftar marang situs-situs iki, misah jeneng nganggo tanda spasi.','Banned Names'=>'Jeneng Sing Diblokir','Allow site administrators to add new users to their site via the "Users &rarr; Add New" page'=>'Ngidinaké admin situs nambah panganggo anyar marang situsé via kācā "Tambah Panganggo &rarr; Anyar"','Add New Users'=>'Nambahaké Panganggo Anyar','Send the network admin an email notification every time someone registers a site or user account'=>'Kirimi admin jaringan email wārā-wārā saben ānā sing ndaftar nang situs utāwā akun panganggo','Registration notification'=>'Cathetan pendaftaran','If registration is disabled, please set %1$s in %2$s to a URL you will redirect visitors to if they visit a non-existent site.'=>'Yén pendaftaran dipaténi, mangga setèl %1$s nang %2$s marang URL kanggo ngalihaké tamu yen dhéwéké niliki situs sing ora cumawis.','Both sites and user accounts can be registered'=>'Situs lan akun panganggo karoné bisā didaftaraké','Logged in users may register new sites'=>'Panganggo sing mlebu log bisā ndaftaraké situs anyar','User accounts may be registered'=>'Akun panganggo mungkin uwis kedaftar','Registration is disabled'=>'Pandaftaran dipaténi','New registrations settings'=>'Setelan pendaftar anyar','Allow new registrations'=>'Ngidinaké pendaftaran anyar','Registration Settings'=>'Pangaturan Pandaftaran','There is a pending change of the network admin email to %s.'=>'Ānā owahan sing ditahan sākā email admin jaringan marang %s.','Operational Settings'=>'Setélan Operasional','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Settings_Screen">Documentation on Network Settings</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Settings_Screen">Dokumentasi kanggo Setèlan Jaringan</a>','Super admins can no longer be added on the Options screen. You must now go to the list of existing users on Network Admin > Users and click on Username or the Edit action link below that name. This goes to an Edit User page where you can check a box to grant super admin privileges.'=>'Super admin ora bisā suwé ditambahaké nang layar Opsi. Sampéyan saiki kudu mlebu nang daftar panganggo sing cumawis nang Admin Jaringan > Panganggo lan klik nang Jeneng panganggo utāwā pranālā Sunting nang ngisor jeneng. Iki bakal nuju marang kācā Sunting Panganggo lan Sampéyan  nyontrèng kotak pilih kanggo ngakui kewenangan super admin.','Menu setting enables/disables the plugin menus from appearing for non super admins, so that only super admins, not site admins, have access to activate plugins.'=>'Pengaturan menu uguripaké/maténi plugin khusus menu nampilaké kanggo non super admin, mulané namung super admin dudu admin situs sing bisā mlebu ngakses kanggo ngaktifaké plugin.','Upload settings control the size of the uploaded files and the amount of available upload space for each site. You can change the default value for specific sites when you edit a particular site. Allowed file types are also listed (space separated only).'=>'Setélan unggahan ngatur ukuran berkas sing diunggah lan jumlah kapasitas unggahan nang saben situs. Sampéyan bisa ngubah biji gawané kanggo situs tinentu nalikā Sampéyan nyunting nang sebagian situs. Jenis-jenis berkas sing diidinaké uga kedaftar (dipisahake nganggo spasi).','New site settings are defaults applied when a new site is created in the network. These include welcome email for when a new site or user account is registered, and what&#8127;s put in the first post, page, comment, comment author, and comment URL.'=>'Setélan situs anyar iku ditrapaké gawan nalikā situs anyar digawé nang jaringan. Iki kalebu email sugeng rawuh kanggo situs anyar utāwā akun panganggo sing ndaftar, lan āpā baé sing dijupuk nang kiriman pos pertama, kācā, komentar, penulis komentar lan URL komentar.','Registration settings can disable/enable public signups. If you let others sign up for a site, install spam plugins. Spaces, not commas, should separate names banned as sites for this network.'=>'Setélan pendaftaran bisa dipaténi/diuripaké kanggo pendaftaran umum. Yèn Sampéyan ngolèhi pendaftaran kanggo situs, pasangānā plugin anti spam. Spasi, titik koma, sing dadi bagian jeneng bakal diblokir nang jaringan iki.','Operational settings has fields for the network&#8217;s name and admin email.'=>'Setélan operasional nduwéni ros-ros kanggo jeneng jaringan lan alamat email.','This screen sets and changes options for the network as a whole. The first site is the main site in the network and network options are pulled from that original site&#8217;s options.'=>'Setélan layar iki lan opsi ngowahi kanggo jaringan sakabéhané. Situs sing pertama kuwi situs utama nang jaringan iki lan opsi jaringan dijupuk sākā opsi situs asliné.','Network Settings'=>'Setelan Jaringan','themeAdd New'=>'Tambah Anyar','Installed Themes'=>'Tema sing dipasang','Themes %s'=>'Tema %s','All Sites'=>'Kabeh Situs','Upgrade Network'=>'Nganyari Jaringan','Updates'=>'Dianyari','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin">Documentation on the Network Admin</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin">Dokumentasi kanggo Admin jaringan</a>','Quick Tasks'=>'Kerja Cepetan','To search for a site, <strong>enter the path or domain</strong>.'=>'Kanggo nggoléki situs, <strong>lebokaké pang utāwā domain</strong>.','To search for a user, <strong>enter an email address or username</strong>. Use a wildcard to search for a partial username, such as user&#42;.'=>'Kanggo nggoléki panganggo, <strong>lebokaké alamat email utāwā jeneng panganggo</strong>. Gunaknā tanda bintang kanggo sapérangan jeneng panganggo, kayata user&#42;.','To search for a user or site, use the search boxes.'=>'Kanggo nggoléki panganggo utāwā situs, gunaknā kothak panggolékan.','To add a new site, <strong>click Create a New Site</strong>.'=>'Kanggo nambah situs anyar, <strong>klik Gawé situs Anyar</strong>.','To add a new user, <strong>click Create a New User</strong>.'=>'Kanggo nambah panganggo anyar, <strong>klik Gawé panganggo Anyar</strong>.','The Right Now widget on this screen provides current user and site counts on your network.'=>'Saiki Widget nang layar iki nampilaké jumlah panganggo lan situs nang jaringan sampéyan.','Modify global network settings'=>'Ngowahi setelan jaringan global','Update your network'=>'Anyari jaringan sampéyan','Install and activate themes or plugins'=>'Pasang lan aktifaké tema utāwā plugin','Add and manage sites or users'=>'Tambah lan natani situs utāwā panganggo','From here you can:'=>'Sākā kéné sampéyan bisā:','Welcome to your Network Admin. This area of the Administration Screens is used for managing all aspects of your Multisite Network.'=>'Sugeng Rawuh nang Admin Jaringan sampéyan. Area Layar Administrasi iki digunakaké kanggo natani sakabéhing perkārā nang Jaringan Multisitus.','Once you complete these steps, your network is enabled and configured. You will have to log in again.'=>'Sepisanan Sampéyan nglengkapi langkah-langkah iki, jaringan Sampéyan dadi urip lan dikonfigurasi. Sampéyan bakal bisa mlebu log manèh.','Add the following to your %1$s file in %2$s, <strong>replacing</strong> other WordPress rules:'=>'Tambahaké iki marang berkas sampéyan  %1$s nang %2$s,  <strong>ngganteni</strong> parāgā WordPress liyané:','To make your installation more secure, you should also add:'=>'Kanggo nguwataké instalasi sampeyan supāyā luwih aman, sampéyan uga kudu nambahi:','These unique authentication keys are also missing from your %s file.'=>'Kunci-kunci pangesahan unik iki ugā ilang sākā berkas %s Sampéyan.','This unique authentication key is also missing from your %s file.'=>'Kunci pangesahan unik iki ugā ilang sākā berkas %s Sampéyan.','That&#8217;s all, stop editing! Happy blogging.'=>'Namung kuwi, stop nyunting! Wilujeng Blogging.','Add the following to your %1$s file in %2$s <strong>above</strong> the line reading %3$s:'=>'Tambahaké iki marang berkas %1$s sampéyan nang  %2$s <strong>ndhuwur</strong> baris %3$s:','We recommend you back up your existing %s file.'=>'Kulā nganjuraké sampéyan gawé salinan cadangan berkas %s.','We recommend you back up your existing %1$s and %2$s files.'=>'Kulā nganjuraké sampéyan gawé salinan cadangan %1$s lan berkas %2$s.','Complete the following steps to enable the features for creating a network of sites.'=>'Jangkepi langkah-langkah iki kanggo nguripaké fitur kanggo nggawé situs jaringan.','Enabling the Network'=>'Nguripaké Jaringan','Please complete the configuration steps. To create a new network, you will need to empty or remove the network database tables.'=>'Mānggā dilengkapi langkah-langkah konfigurasi iki. Kanggo gawé jaringan anyar, sampéyan kudu ngosongaké utāwā mbuwang tabel database jaringan.','An existing WordPress network was detected.'=>'Ānā jaringan Wordpress sing kedetèksi.','The original configuration steps are shown here for reference.'=>'Langkah-langkah konfigurasi asli ditontonaké nang kéné kanggo rujukan.','Your email address.'=>'Alamat email Sampéyan.','Network Admin Email'=>'Email Admin Jaringan','What would you like to call your network?'=>'Āpā sing sampéyan senengi kanggo nyebut jaringan sampéyan?','Network Title'=>'Jeneng Jaringan','Because your installation is not new, the sites in your WordPress network must use sub-domains.'=>'Mergā instalasi sampéyan ora anyar, situs iki nang jaringan WordPress kudu nganggo sub-domain.','Sub-domain Installation'=>'Instalasi nang sub-domain','Because your installation is in a directory, the sites in your WordPress network must use sub-directories.'=>'Mergā instalasi sampéyan manggon nang direktori, situs iki nang jaringan WordPress kudu nganggo sub-direktori.','The main site in a sub-directory installation will need to use a modified permalink structure, potentially breaking existing links.'=>'Situs utāmā sing dipasang nang sub-direktori kudu nganggo struktur permalink sing dimodifikasi, yèn ora bisā ngrusak pranālā-pranālā sing cumawis.','Because you are using %1$s, the sites in your WordPress network must use sub-directories. Consider using %2$s if you wish to use sub-domains.'=>'Amargā sampéyan nganggo %1$s, situs nang jaringan WordPress iki kudu nganggo sub-direktori. Dipikir dhisik nganggo %2$s yen sampéyan nganggo sub-domain.','Sub-directory Installation'=>'Instalasi nang sub-direktori','Network Details'=>'Detil Jaringan','The internet address of your network will be %s.'=>'Alamat internet sākā jaringan sampéyan dadiné %s.','We recommend you change your siteurl to %1$s before enabling the network feature. It will still be possible to visit your site using the %3$s prefix with an address like %2$s but any links will not have the %3$s prefix.'=>'Kulā nganjuraken sampéyan ngganti alamat url-situs marang %1$s sakdurungé nguripaké fitur jaringan. Iki tetep bisā kanggo niliki situs sampéyan nganggo ater-ater %3$s karo alamat kāyā %2$s nanging saperangan pranālā bakal ora nduwéni ater-ater %3$s.','Server Address'=>'Alamat Server','Subdirectory networks may not be fully compatible with custom wp-content directories.'=>'Subdirektori jaringan mungkin ora bisa kompatibel kabèh karo direktori racikan wp-content.','subdirectory exampleslike <code>%1$s/site1</code> and <code>%1$s/site2</code>'=>'mirip <code>%1$s/site1</code> lan <code>%1$s/site2</code>','Sub-directories'=>'Sub-direktori','subdomain exampleslike <code>site1.%1$s</code> and <code>site2.%1$s</code>'=>'mirip <code>site1.%1$s</code> lan <code>site2.%1$s</code>','Sub-domains'=>'Sub-domains','You will need a wildcard DNS record if you are going to use the virtual host (sub-domain) functionality.'=>'Sampéyan mbutuhaké rekod DNS wildcard yèn Sampéyan arep nganggo virtual host (sub-domain) dadi fungsi.','You cannot change this later.'=>'Sampéyan ora bisā ngubah iki maneh.','Please choose whether you would like sites in your WordPress network to use sub-domains or sub-directories.'=>'Mangga dipilih sampéyan arep nganggo situs Jaringan WordPress nang sub-domain utāwā nang sub-direktori.','Addresses of Sites in your Network'=>'Alamat situs-situs nang Jaringan sampéyan','If %1$s is disabled, ask your administrator to enable that module, or look at the <a href="%2$s">Apache documentation</a> or <a href="%3$s">elsewhere</a> for help setting it up.'=>'Yèn %1$s dipaténi, takonānā administrator Sampéyan kanggo nguripaké modul kuwi, utāwā ndeleng nang <a href="%2$s">Dokumentasi Apache </a> utāwā <a href="%3$s">nang endi waé</a> kanggo mbantu nyetèl.','It looks like the Apache %s module is not installed.'=>'Ketoké modul Apache %s ora dipasang.','Please make sure the Apache %s module is installed as it will be used at the end of this installation.'=>'Mangga dipastekaké modul Apache %s uwis dipasang dadi bisā dienggo nganti rampunge pamasangan.','Fill in the information below and you&#8217;ll be on your way to creating a network of WordPress sites. We will create configuration files in the next step.'=>'Isènānā informasi nang ngisor iki lan Sampéyan bakal nang alur gawé jaringan nang situs WordPress. Kitā sing bakal nggawé berkas konfigurasiné nang langkah saklanjuté.','Welcome to the Network installation process!'=>'Sugeng Rawuh marang proses pemasangan Jaringan!','%s Sites'=>'%s Situs','ERROR: The network could not be created.'=>'KALUPUTAN: Jaringan ora bisā digawe.','Return to Dashboard'=>'Mbalik nang Dasbor','You cannot use port numbers such as %s.'=>'Sampéyan ora bisā nganggo nomer port kayadéné %s.','You cannot install a network of sites with your server address.'=>'Sampéyan ora bisā masang situs jaringan ngango alamat server sampéyan.','Once the network is created, you may reactivate your plugins.'=>'Sepisan waé jaringan digawé, sampéyan bisa ngaktifaké plugin sampéyan.','Please <a href="%s">deactivate your plugins</a> before enabling the Network feature.'=>'Mānggā<a href="%s">non-aktifaké plugin sampéyan</a> sakdurungé nguripaké fitur Jaringan.','Warning:'=>'Weling:','The constant %s cannot be defined when creating a network.'=>'Konstanta %s ora bisā terangaké nalikā gawé jaringan.','userRegistered'=>'Kedhaftar','Super Admin <span class="count">(%s)</span>'=>'Super Admin <span class="count">(%s)</s